A program to get a dump of the heap at the initialization of the JVM (before
the CLINIT of the class containing the main method).

In order to run it the following environment variables must be set:
  - JAVA_HOME : set to a jvm dir.
  - LD_LIBRARY_PATH must include the directory where is libHeapInspector.so is
    located.

#### Compile it ####
  make 

#### Get a dump for the minimal program ####
  make run

#### Get a dump for personalized program ####
  java -agentlib:HeapInspector="pkg.MainClass" pkg.MainClass

